  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网边缘节点的评论审核流程设计一个状态图。核心场景是：操作员通过MQTT Broker提交评论，然后经过审核才能控制执行器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那评论创建之后，是先进入一个待处理状态吗？我理解为需要先经过EdgeNode的审核，再决定是放行到PLC逻辑还是隐藏？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Pending是入口状态。在Pending内部，评论先进入AwaitingModeration子状态，由EdgeNode负责审核。审核通过走Approved分支，被拒绝走Rejected分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主状态结构画出来：从MQTT Broker创建评论进入Pending，Pending可以Approve到Approved、Reject到Rejected，或者Delete直接删除。Approved和Rejected也都可以Delete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要细化Approved和Rejected的内部状态。Approved的评论应该是Visible可见状态，并且可以Edit编辑；Rejected的要先Hidden隐藏，然后可以Add Rejection Reason添加拒绝原因。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下流转关系：Visible编辑后变成Edited，Edited更新后再回到Visible，形成循环？还有WithReason之后是流向PLC Logic吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "WithReason",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。另外Deleted状态的评论最终要流转到ActuatorController执行物理删除动作。Pending内部的AwaitingModeration也要关联回EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Deleted",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构完成了。我给四个主状态加上注释说明：Pending标注评论等待审核，Approved标注可见且可编辑，Rejected标注隐藏并带拒绝原因，Deleted标注永久移除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查一遍没问题。这个状态图完整覆盖了从MQTT Broker提交、EdgeNode审核、PLC Logic处理到ActuatorController执行的完整工业评论管理流程。",
